	quests: [
		{
			description: [
				"Vanilla combat is just the start."
				""
				"§bSimply Swords§r adds over a dozen new weapon types \u2014 Longswords, Claymores, War Scythes, Katanas, Chakrams and more. Craft them like vanilla swords using the same material tiers: Iron \u2192 Diamond \u2192 Netherite \u2192 Runic."
				""
				"§bBetter Combat§r overhauls attack animations and lets you dual-wield any two weapons. Put a weapon in your offhand and attack to combo with both."
				""
				"§6Relics§r and §6Artifacts§r provide passive and active powers found in dungeon loot and mob drops."
				""
				"Face every threat \u2014 overworld mobs, Nether bosses, the End, Cataclysm, and the Aether's dungeons."
			]
			icon: "minecraft:netherite_sword"
			id: "F000"
			optional: true
			size: 1.5d
			subtitle: "Click to learn more"
			tasks: [{
				id: "F100"
				title: "Combat \& Adventure Overview"
				type: "checkmark"
			}]
			title: "§6\u2694 Combat \& Adventure"
			x: 0.0d
			y: 0.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["F000"]
			description: [
				"§bSimply Swords§r adds a range of weapon types beyond the vanilla sword."
				""
				"The §9Longsword§r has excellent reach. The §9Claymore§r is a heavy two-hander. The §9War Scythe§r sweeps wide \u2014 great against crowds."
				""
				"Craft them exactly like a vanilla sword \u2014 same recipe shape, same material tiers. The §aRunic§r tier is the highest craftable tier."
			]
			id: "F001"
			rewards: [{
				id: "F201"
				item: "simplyswords:iron_longsword"
				type: "item"
			}]
			subtitle: "New weapons for a classic game"
			tasks: [{
				id: "F101"
				title: "Craft any Simply Swords weapon"
				type: "checkmark"
			}]
			title: "Simply Armed"
			x: -4.0d
			y: -3.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["F000"]
			description: [
				"§bBetter Combat§r lets you put a weapon in your offhand and attack with both hands in sequence."
				""
				"Different weapon combos play differently \u2014 try a sword in your main hand and a shorter weapon offhand for rapid alternating hits."
				""
				"Blocking now has a cooldown, so good offence matters far more than shield-spam."
			]
			id: "F002"
			rewards: [{
				id: "F202"
				item: "minecraft:shield"
				type: "item"
			}]
			subtitle: "Two weapons, one enemy"
			tasks: [{
				id: "F102"
				title: "Dual-wield two weapons and land a hit"
				type: "checkmark"
			}]
			title: "Dual Threat"
			x: -2.0d
			y: -3.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["F000"]
			description: [
				"§6Relics§r are magical items found in dungeon loot, mob drops, or crafted via special recipes."
				""
				"Each Relic has a unique ability \u2014 some grant passive stat boosts, others have active skills triggered by right-clicking."
				""
				"Some Relics require researching before their powers unlock. Open the Relics menu to track your collection and research progress."
			]
			id: "F003"
			rewards: [{
				id: "F203"
				item: "relics:leather_belt"
				type: "item"
			}]
			subtitle: "Power hides in old ruins"
			tasks: [{
				id: "F103"
				title: "Find any Relic item"
				type: "checkmark"
			}]
			title: "First Relic"
			x: 0.0d
			y: -3.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["F003"]
			description: [
				"§6Artifacts§r are rare trinkets found in dungeon chests, mineshafts, strongholds, and structures."
				""
				"Unlike Relics, Artifacts are purely passive \u2014 equip them in a §bCurios§r slot and their effect activates automatically."
				""
				"Look for §aFeral Claws§r (faster attack speed), §aCloud in a Bottle§r (double jump), or §aFire Gauntlet§r (ignite enemies on hit)."
			]
			id: "F004"
			rewards: [{
				id: "F204"
				item: "artifacts:feral_claws"
				type: "item"
			}]
			subtitle: "Trinkets with teeth"
			tasks: [{
				id: "F104"
				title: "Equip any Artifact in a Curios slot"
				type: "checkmark"
			}]
			title: "Artifact Hunter"
			x: 2.0d
			y: -3.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["F000"]
			description: [
				"Spiders are common but don't underestimate them \u2014 they climb walls, move fast, and inflict Poison in caves."
				""
				"Spider Jockeys spawn infrequently with a Skeleton rider. Night fights near cave entrances can get messy fast."
				""
				"Equip a §aCross Necklace§r (found in dungeons) to survive otherwise lethal hits \u2014 a strong early-game Artifact trinket."
			]
			id: "F010"
			rewards: [{
				id: "F210"
