		{
			dependencies: ["F011"]
			description: [
				"Skeletons are accurate at range \u2014 close the distance fast or fight them from cover."
				""
				"§bArchers§r mod adds new bow and crossbow variants with different range, reload speed, and damage profiles. Outrange them with a Composite Longbow."
				""
				"Use a §9War Scythe§r or §9Greataxe§r to interrupt their shots in melee. A shield on a timed raise also deflects arrows."
