		{
			dependencies: ["F012"]
			description: [
				"Drowned lurk in rivers, oceans, and flooded ruins. Those with Tridents will throw them \u2014 watch for the wind-up before they release."
				""
				"Underwater combat is slowed without Aqua Affinity and Depth Strider. Fight on the surface edge where possible."
				""
				"§aAqua Dashers§r grant superior underwater movement \u2014 essential for ocean monuments, shipwrecks, and any deep-water fight."
