			description: [
				"Blazes guard Nether Fortresses with relentless fireball barrages."
				""
				"Use a Composite Longbow or Heavy Crossbow from §bArchers§r to fight them from range. Alternatively \u2014 close in fast with a two-handed weapon to interrupt their attack charge."
				""
