			description: [
				"Ghasts wander open Nether skies and lob explosive fireballs at anything they spot."
				""
				"Their fireballs can be knocked back with a hit \u2014 deflecting one back into the Ghast kills it in one shot. A longbow is more reliable for consistent range kills."
				""
				"Ghast Tears drop rarely and are irreplaceable \u2014 needed for Potions of Regeneration and End Crystals."
